{
  "text": "JMJD6 possibly engages multiple pathways to increase cell proliferation JMJD6 suppressed TGF-b2 expression and cell proliferation in both MCF-7 and MDA-MB 231 cells. However, TGF-\u03b22 mediates cell-cycle arrest only in MCF-7 cells, but not in MDA-MB 231, T47D, and CAMA-1 cells [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . Therefore, TGF-\u03b22 may not be the mediator of ",
